    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving masterpiece. Under the hood, the S54B32 inline-six remains a marvel of engineering, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce an exhilarating 333 hp. The power is managed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a M-Variable Lock differential. This chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a recent rod bearing service, ensuring the structural and internal integrity required for spirited driving. Suspension is composed of a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, currently optimized with upgraded bushings for sharpened turn-in. While the exterior shows honest wear, the drivetrain and cooling system are in excellent health, offering the quintessential analog driving experience with the precision of a well-maintained M-car.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. Minor exterior wear. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and presents beautifully in its original factory finish. The exterior retains a deep luster, showing only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, while the dashboard and trim are preserved without sun damage or cracking. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule\u2014gear shifts are seamless, the engine provides smooth power delivery, and the braking is firm and responsive. Recently fitted with high-quality tires and having just passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this car offers a refined driving experience for a buyer who values both reliability and aesthetic appeal.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle represents a superb balance of performance and meticulous upkeep. It has been curated for the discerning driver who demands mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic. Demonstrating clear pride of ownership, the interior and exterior remain in commendable state, offering a sophisticated driving experience that aligns with our rigorous standards for quality. This is an exceptional opportunity to secure a premium asset that delivers both longevity and prestige.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
