      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It has been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape, making it perfect for anyone who needs a dependable set of wheels that's ready to hit the road today! It drives smoothly and has been well-loved. I'd love for you to come take a look and see for yourself how great it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to help!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
