      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six engine, boasting individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system for optimized valve timing. This chassis remains structurally sound and composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings throughout the multi-link suspension. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox provides crisp, tactile engagement, transferring power through a variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. Recently serviced with 10W-60 synthetic lubricant, this unit delivers linear power delivery all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically sorted example ready for the apex.",
